InternationalPhoenix Energy Corp said it launched a gold recovery venturewith &lt;Phoenix Exploration and Recovery Inc> and Mexico'sSistemas Tecnicos De Recuperaciones, Sociedad Anonima deCapital Variable.    The company said the joint venture will explore and recovergold, precious metals and artefacts from treasure ships worth10 billion dlrs reported to have sunk in the harbor area ofVera Cruz, Mexico.    The company said it expects work to begin in 30 days. Reuter&#3;